notes.note: Rec'd additional request for replacement of all 4 calipers. Front and rear. Mentioned that all caliper pins are seized. Spoke with Adam about a similar case previously, mentioned we will not cover calipers if slider pins are seized. Called Guelph Nissan, said Nissan does not technically have brake services as a required repair, however, if a customer came in with all 4 slider pins seized within the applicable basic 3 year 60/000 km warranty, they would decline the warranty repair request based off of insufficient brake maintenance. Described concern for this client, confirmed they would deny it based off of insufficient maintenance. Declining this additional repair request. M.P.
